**A Culinary Experience to Remember: De AB's Catering**

De AB's catering brought perfection to our cradle ceremony, making the event truly unforgettable. The food, service, and stunning setup were nothing short of exceptional. The carefully curated menu included an exquisite range of dishes that delighted every palate. From the tangy **Paneer Chilly** to the richly spiced **Chicken Kerala Fry**, every appetizer was a burst of flavor. The succulent **Juicy Chicken** and creamy **Chicken Malai Tikka** were crowd favorites.

For the mains, the fragrant **Veg Pulav** and flavorful **Chicken Biryani** paired beautifully with the indulgent **Veg Korma** and the regal **Chicken Mughlai**, offering a perfect balance of vegetarian and non-vegetarian options. To end the meal on a sweet note, the crispy **Jalebi** and creamy **Kulfi** were absolute showstoppers, leaving everyone craving more.

The setup was a visual treat, combining elegance and functionality. The golden accents, intricately designed panels, and warm lighting created an inviting ambiance that enhanced the celebration. Every detail, from the artistic plating to the seamless organization, reflected De AB's commitment to excellence.

If you're looking for a catering service that guarantees delicious food, impeccable presentation, and a hassle-free experience, De AB's is the ultimate choice. They truly made our special day extraordinary!

I would like to thank Mr ABRAR SHAIKH the owner of DE AB'S CATERING for making my brother wedding so memorable.the food was mouth watering specially chicken dum biryani and top notch was chicken Kerala fry.they had done a excellent job with food , setup and service. Would like to congratulate hole team of DE AB'S CATERING for there finominal work.we will suggest you to people in future may God bless you all thanks ones again
